high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up the spoon that is in the sink behind the apple.
With the spoon in hand turn and go to the counter where the wine bottles are.
Place the spoon in the cup that is right in front of the paper bag.
Pick up the cup that has the spoon in it.
With the cup with the spoon in hand turn and go to the sink.
Place the cup with the spoon in it in to the sink to the left of the apple and the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place spoon in cup to place in sink.

high_descs: Head towards the sink
Pick up the spoon in the sink
Turn right then face the sink counter on your right
Put the spoon in the glass on the counter
Pick up the glass with spoon
Turn left then head to the sink
Put the glass with spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the glass with spoon in the sink

high_descs: Move forward to the sink.
Pick up the silver spoon in the sink.
Bring the spoon to the counter, right of the sink.
Put the spoon in the orange cup on the back of the counter.
Pick up the orange cup with spoon on the back of the counter.
Bring the cup with spoon to the sink on left.
Put the cup with spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a spoon in it, in the sink.
